  "type": "Section",
  "number": "2.5",
  "title": "HTML Quiz",
  "body": " HTML Quiz  Do NOT click on the start button until you are ready to take this quiz. (probably during class) Once you open the quiz you are committed to finishing it. The quiz has a time limit of 20 minutes.     Q-1: What does HTML stand for?      Hyperlinks and Text Markup Language    None      Hyper Text Markup Language    None      Home Tool Markup Language    None        Q-2: Choose the correct HTML element for the largest heading:      <h6>    None      <head>    None      <heading>    None      <h1>    None        Q-3: What is the correct HTML element for inserting a line break?      <br>    None      <break>    None      <lb>    None        Q-4: What is the correct HTML for creating a hyperlink?      <a>http:\/\/www.w3schools.com<\/a>    None      <a href=\"http:\/\/www.w3schools.com\">W3Schools<\/a>    None      <a name=\"http:\/\/www.w3schools.com\">W3Schools.com<\/a>    None      <a url=\"http:\/\/www.w3schools.com\">W3Schools.com<\/a>    None        Q-5: Which character is used to indicate an end tag?      *    None      \/    None      <    None      ^    None        Q-6: Which of these elements are all &lt;table&gt; elements?      <table><tr><td>    None      <table><head><tfoot>    None      <thead><body><tr>    None      <table><tr><tt>    None        Q-7: Inline elements are normally displayed without starting a new line.      True    None      False    None        Q-8: How can you make a numbered list?      <dl>    None      <ul>    None      <list>    None      <ol>    None        Q-9: What is the correct HTML for inserting an image?      <image src=\"image.gif\" alt=\"MyImage\">    None      <img href=\"image.gif\" alt=\"MyImage\">    None      <img src=\"image.gif\" alt=\"MyImage\">    None      <img alt=\"MyImage\">image.gif<\/img>    None        Q-10: Block elements are normally displayed without starting a new line.      False    None      True    None        Q-11: Which HTML element defines the title of a document?      <meta>    None      <head>    None      <title>    None      <h1>    None       Once you have completed the quiz you can review your answers but you will not be able to change them.  "
